longBusinessSummary: R3 Score Technologies, Inc. develops a data driven scoring tool for criminal background screenings. The company offers a software-as-a-service (SaaS) software product, R3 Score, which predicts productivity, competency, and risk level of criminal-background individuals for lenders and employers. It serves banks, landlords, colleges and universities, and financial institutions. The company was founded in 2017 and is based in Baltimore, Maryland.
